                                                                                      InputBuilderListener inputBuilderListener)
        Create or update an MacroscopicLinkSegmentTypeXmlHelper object using the input from the current row in the XML input file If the mode number is 0, all modes are updated
        Parameters:
        name - link type name
        capacityPerLane - capacity per lane
        maximumDensityPerLane - maximum density per lane
        maxSpeed - maximum speed
        critSpeed - critical speed
        modeExternalId - reference to the mode used in the XML input file
        linkTypeExternalId - id number of the link type
        inputBuilderListener - parser containing Map of modes by external Id
        Returns:
        MacroscopicLinkSegmentTypeXmlHelper object, created or updated to include data from current row in the XML file
